{"id":7819,"date":"2025-12-29T13:30:47","date_gmt":"2025-12-29T06:30:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7819"},"modified":"2026-01-05T09:38:55","modified_gmt":"2026-01-05T02:38:55","slug":"sulfur-la-gi-cong-dung","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/sulfur-la-gi-cong-dung\/","title":{"rendered":"Sulfur \u2013 Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 d\u00e0y s\u1eebng da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sulfur, hay l\u01b0u hu\u1ef3nh, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong y h\u1ecdc da li\u1ec5u. T\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 15, sulfur \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m da \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sulfur v\u1eabn gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1edd t\u00ednh kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m d\u00e0y s\u1eebng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-sulfur\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Sulfur<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sulfur l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean t\u1ed1 vi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (k\u00fd hi\u1ec7u S, s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean t\u1eed 16), xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u2014 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf t\u00f3c, m\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 keratin da. D\u1ea1ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 Sulfur k\u1ebft t\u1ee7a (Precipitated Sulfur) ho\u1eb7c Colloidal Sulfur, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tinh khi\u1ebft cao v\u00e0 \u00edt m\u00f9i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng th\u00f4.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sulfur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong \u0111\u00e1 n\u00fai l\u1eeda, su\u1ed1i kho\u00e1ng, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 amino acid (methionine, cysteine). \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng da li\u1ec5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 XIX v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n (OTC).<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7821\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7821\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7821 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-1.webp\" alt=\"Sulfur c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7821\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sulfur c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-sulfur-trong-da-lieu\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Sulfur trong da li\u1ec5u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 \u2013 v\u1eeba:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, gom c\u1ed3i nhanh, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam s\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m da \u0111\u1ea7u:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> nh\u1edd t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1ng n\u1ea5m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, sulfur c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c \u1ed5 vi\u00eam tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Gi\u1ea3m d\u00e0y s\u1eebng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng (keratosis pilaris):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m da, gi\u1ea3m s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Sulfur, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u00e0y s\u1eebng nang l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i c\u00f9ng BHA, Resorcinol, ho\u1eb7c Sodium sulfacetamide. <\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-co-che-hoat-dong-cua-sulfur\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m &amp; C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Sulfur<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Keratolytic (l\u00e0m bong s\u1eebng):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Sulfur ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi cysteine trong l\u1edbp s\u1eebng t\u1ea1o acid pentathionic, gi\u00fap ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i disulfide trong keratin \u2192 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, l\u00e0m th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n &amp; kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Sulfur c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf Cutibacterium acnes (vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n) v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u1ee8c ch\u1ebf nh\u1eb9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nh\u1eddn v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kh\u00e1ng n\u1ea5m:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean <\/span><b>Malassezia spp.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p trong vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ea5m.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_7822\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7822\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7822 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-2.webp\" alt=\"Sulful \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7822\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sulful \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Theo FDA OTC Monograph M006 (2021), Sulfur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n (OTC) \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 3\u201310%.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kem ho\u1eb7c gel ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n (spot treatment):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u1ee9a ~3\u201310% sulfur.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng sulfur:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 5\u201310%, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9, gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 b\u00f9n ch\u1ee9a sulfur:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam nhanh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Dung d\u1ecbch r\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c lotion:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> d\u00f9ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n l\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-thuc-phoi-hop-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Sulfur + Salicylic Acid (BHA):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u201cb\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng\u201d gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u \u2013 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam \u2013 gom c\u1ed3i nhanh. Trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, ti\u00eau c\u00f4i m\u1ee5n \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t. Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1c s\u1eebng ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Sulfur + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 <\/span>gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Sulfur + Zinc PCA:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u00e1t khu\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Sulfur + Tranexamic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u00eam v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-mun-gsc\/\"><b>Xem ngay: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum m\u1ee5n Sulfur+BHA GSC<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"v-luu-y-chong-chi-dinh\"><\/span><b>V. L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7823\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7823\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7823 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-3.webp\" alt=\"Khi d\u00f9ng sulful c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd g\u00ec\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/87-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7823\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 Sulfur v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng chung v\u1edbi Resorcinol n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao ho\u1eb7c Benzoyl Peroxide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y bong \u0111\u1ecf m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0u da t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p (2\u20133 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Tr\u00e1nh b\u00f4i di\u1ec7n r\u1ed9ng (\u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ea1ng spot treatment):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng v\u00f9ng da d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Tr\u00e1nh v\u00f9ng m\u1eaft, m\u00f4i, ni\u00eam m\u1ea1c.<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>M\u00f9i \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u01b0u hu\u1ef3nh c\u00f3 m\u00f9i tr\u1ee9ng tanh nh\u1eb9 \u2013 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu\u1ed1c tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a Sulfur kh\u00f4ng?<\/b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">An to\u00e0n khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 to\u00e0n th\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean tham v\u1ea5n \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00ec s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd.<\/span><b><br \/>\n<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u01a1i tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, tr\u00e1nh nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao; kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 sulfur ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac l\u00e2u v\u1edbi kim lo\u1ea1i (d\u1ec5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0u).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Brasted, R. (2019). sulfur | Definition, Properties, Uses, &amp; Facts. In Encyclopaedia Britannica.<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.britannica.com\/science\/sulfur\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> https:\/\/www.britannica.com\/science\/sulfur<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U.S. Food and Drug Administration Over-the-Counter (OTC) Monograph M006: Topical Acne Drug Products for Over-the-Counter Human Use (Posted November 23, 2021) 1 Part A-General Provisions Part A-General Provisions \u00a7 M006.1 Scope. (n.d.). <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.accessdata.fda.gov\/drugsatfda_docs\/omuf\/monographs\/OTC%20Monograph_M006-Topical%20Acne%20drug%20products%20for%20OTC%20Human%20Use%2011.23.2021.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">https:\/\/www.accessdata.fda.gov\/drugsatfda_docs\/omuf\/monographs\/OTC%20Monograph_M006-Topical%20Acne%20drug%20products%20for%20OTC%20Human%20Use%2011.23.2021.pdf<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200c<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sulfur, hay l\u01b0u hu\u1ef3nh, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong y h\u1ecdc da li\u1ec5u. T\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 15, sulfur \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m da \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sulfur v\u1eabn gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1edd t\u00ednh kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m d\u00e0y s\u1eebng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7824,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7819","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7819","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7819"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7819\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7994,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7819\/revisions\/7994"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7824"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7819"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7819"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7819"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}